name: Nuttcp-Cygwin-GUI
short_description:
GUI frontend for Nuttcp. Nuttcp-Cygwin-GUI is a user-friendly network performance test tool with graphical user interface.

Nuttcp is a popular network performance test tool. The homepage of Nuttcp is: http://www.nuttcp.net/nuttcp/Welcome%20Page.html.

Please refer to this website for more info about Nuttcp: http://www.wcisd.hpc.mil/nuttcp/Nuttcp-HOWTO.html.

The objective of this project is to develop a user-friendly network performance test tool with graphical user interface. The GUI of Nuttcp-Cygwin-GUI is based on Jperf.
summary: Nuttcp-Cygwin-GUI is a GUI frontend for Nuttcp.
